      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DAYTONA (1) could not have been more impressive last start in his a head turning 25.26 win at this track over 457m. In winning form and can measure up again. ICE RIDER (2) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at Capalaba over 366m behind Rupesh (20.22) in a Restricted WIN. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. MILCHICK (3) doesn't show much early dash but winds into his races, two back missing the frame but last time hitting the line hard to place when third (25.93) in a Restricted WIN at this track last time. Expecting another good run. SPRING FLICK (8) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when second (25.56) in a Restricted WIN over 457m at this track.",
